// All ability data lives in this single file. IDs are packed (level << 8 | sub),
// so I keep one "level" byte per character to make it obvious who owns what:
//
//   0x00 — generic / placeholder demo abilities
//   0x0A — Rina        (ids 2560..)
//   0x0B — Sayaka      (ids 2816..)
//   0x0C — Houjou Utaka (ids 3072..)
//   0x0D — Toshiko     (ids 3328..)
//   0x0F — Yokai       (ids 3840..)
//
// Effects use the new `ApplyStatus { kind, tier }` / `RemoveStatus { kind }`
// variants for non-damage actions (Cleanse, Bind spirit, Whisper, etc.).
[
